<text>Xiong may refer to:

==Name==
* Xiong (surname) (熊), a Chinese surname

==Location==
* Xiong County, in Hebei, China

==Language==
* The pinyin romanization of several Chinese characters, including (elder brother), (chest), (heroic) and (bear)
* The Xong language and the Miao people who speak it

==Group==
* Xong, or Limbu people
* A subdivision of the Mongol armies: see Huns</text><links>
