* Jakob Axel Nielsen (born 1967), Danish lawyer and politician
* Jakob Nielsen (actor) (1900-1978)
* Jacob Nielsen (cyclist) (born 1978), Danish cyclist
* Jakob Ahlmann Nielsen (born 1991), Danish footballer</text><links>
